{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "a1b2c3d4-e5f6-47a8-9b0c-examen-dad-u2",
    "name": "Examen DAD - Unidad 2 (Academia de Talleres)",
    "description": "Coleccion completa de los microservicios de la Academia de Talleres.\n\n**Arquitectura:** Spring Boot 3.5.14 + Spring Cloud 2025.0.2 (Eureka, Config Server, Gateway, OpenFeign).\n\nTodas las peticiones pasan por el **API Gateway** ({{gateway}} = http://localhost:8080), que enruta hacia cada microservicio registrado en Eureka.\n\n| Microservicio | Puerto | Base de datos |\n|---|---|---|\n| ms-gestion-instructor | 8081 | db_instructor |\n| ms-gestion-alumno | 8082 | db_alumno |\n| ms-gestion-taller (compuesto) | 8083 | db_taller |\n\n**Orden de arranque:** Eureka (8761) -> Config (8888) -> Gateway (8080) -> Instructor -> Alumno -> Taller.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "0. Seguridad (Auth)",
      "description": "Microservicio **ms-seguridad** (puerto 8084, BD `db_seguridad`). Maneja usuarios, roles y permisos, y emite tokens **JWT**.\n\nUsa `Login` o `Register`: el token devuelto se guarda automaticamente en la variable de entorno `{{token}}` y se envia como `Bearer` en todas las demas peticiones (auth heredada a nivel de coleccion).\n\nUsuario administrador creado al arrancar: **admin / admin123**.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register (Alumno)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const data = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (data && data.token) {",
                  "  pm.environment.set('token', data.token);",
                  "  console.log('Token guardado en {{token}}');",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"luis\",\n  \"correo\": \"luis@correo.com\",\n  \"password\": \"alumno123\",\n  \"rol\": \"ALUMNO\",\n  \"nombres\": \"Luis\",\n  \"apellidos\": \"Gomez\",\n  \"dni\": \"70123456\",\n  \"telefono\": \"999111222\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{gateway}}/api/auth/register",
              "host": ["{{gateway}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "register"]
            },
            "description": "Registra una cuenta con rol ALUMNO y crea automaticamente su ficha en ms-gestion-alumno (requiere dni). Devuelve el JWT (se guarda en {{token}}) e idReferencia = id de la ficha."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Register (Instructor)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const data = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (data && data.token) {",
                  "  pm.environment.set('token', data.token);",
                  "  console.log('Token guardado en {{token}}');",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"ana\",\n  \"correo\": \"ana@academia.com\",\n  \"password\": \"instru123\",\n  \"rol\": \"INSTRUCTOR\",\n  \"nombres\": \"Ana\",\n  \"apellidos\": \"Torres\",\n  \"especialidad\": \"Pintura\",\n  \"telefono\": \"987654321\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{gateway}}/api/auth/register",
              "host": ["{{gateway}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "register"]
            },
            "description": "Registra una cuenta con rol INSTRUCTOR y crea automaticamente su ficha en ms-gestion-instructor (requiere especialidad). Devuelve el JWT (se guarda en {{token}}) e idReferencia = id de la ficha."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (Admin)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const data = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (data && data.token) {",
                  "  pm.environment.set('token', data.token);",
                  "  console.log('Token guardado en {{token}}');",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"admin\",\n  \"password\": \"admin123\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{gateway}}/api/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{gateway}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "login"]
            },
            "description": "Inicia sesion con el administrador creado al arrancar (admin / admin123). El token se guarda en {{token}}."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const data = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (data && data.token) {",
                  "  pm.environment.set('token', data.token);",
                  "  console.log('Token guardado en {{token}}');",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"luis\",\n  \"password\": \"alumno123\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{gateway}}/api/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{gateway}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "login"]
            },
            "description": "Inicia sesion con cualquier usuario. El token devuelto se guarda en {{token}}."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Listar usuarios (solo ADMIN)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{gateway}}/api/usuarios",
              "host": ["{{gateway}}"],
              "path": ["api", "usuarios"]
            },
            "description": "Lista todos los usuarios. Requiere un token con rol ADMIN (inicia sesion con admin primero)."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
